### Cadastrar cliente 1
POST http://localhost:8080/clientes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Misael Dutra",
  "email": "misael@gmail.com",
  "telefone": "(74) 99999-9999",
  "senha": "12345678",
  "cpf": "12345678900"
}

### Cadastrar cliente 2
POST http://localhost:8080/clientes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Ana Souza",
  "email": "ana@gmail.com",
  "telefone": "(74) 98888-8888",
  "senha": "87654321",
  "cpf": "98765432100"
}

### Listar clientes
GET http://localhost:8080/clientes

### Listar clientes com paginação
GET http://localhost:8080/clientes?page=0&size=5&sort=nome,asc

### Buscar cliente por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/clientes/1

### Buscar cliente inexistente
GET http://localhost:8080/clientes/999

### Atualizar cliente
PUT http://localhost:8080/clientes/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Misael Carvalho Dutra",
  "email": "misaelnovo@gmail.com",
  "telefone": "(74) 97777-7777",
  "senha": "12345678",
  "cpf": "12345678900"
}

### Teste validação
POST http://localhost:8080/clientes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "",
  "email": "email-invalido",
  "telefone": "",
  "senha": "123",
  "cpf": ""
}

### Teste email duplicado
POST http://localhost:8080/clientes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Carlos Lima",
  "email": "misael@gmail.com",
  "telefone": "(74) 96666-6666",
  "senha": "12345678",
  "cpf": "11122233344"
}

### Deletar cliente
DELETE http://localhost:8080/clientes/1